      "content": "hope? there's no hope. i've tried everything and it just gets worse. it's like the more i try to be okay, the more they find ways to tear me down. it feels like there's just no point in trying to fix something that's so fundamentally broken. i feel like i'm just trapped in this nightmare and there's no way to wake up from it.",
